## Design Philosophy

**Before (Bad):**
- Fixed-height containers everywhere
- `h-full` cascade from root to leaf
- `overflow-hidden` prevents scrolling
- Special cases break other pages

**After (Good):**
- Normal document flow by default
- Main tag scrolls (`overflow-y-auto`)
- Special cases isolated (Planning uses `calc()`)
- Predictable scrolling behavior

